+config AIROHA_EN7571
+	tristate "Airoha EN7571 PON laser driver IC"
+	depends on I2C && HWMON
+	help
+	  Support for the Airoha EN7571 PON laser driver IC used in
+	  GPON/EPON/xPON optical transceivers (Airoha EN75xx SoC family).
+
+	  Provides SFF-8472 Digital Diagnostic Monitoring Interface (DDMI)
+	  via hwmon: temperature, supply voltage, bias current, Tx and Rx
+	  optical power.  Also exposes xpon_mode and los sysfs attributes.
+
+	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here.
+
+config AIROHA_EN7570
+	tristate "Airoha EN7570 BOSA laser driver IC"
+	depends on I2C && HWMON
+	select REGMAP
+	help
+	  Support for the Airoha EN7570 BOSA (Burst Optical Sub-Assembly)
+	  laser driver IC used in optical transceivers.
+
+	  Provides SFF-8472 Digital Diagnostic Monitoring Interface (DDMI)
+	  via hwmon: temperature, supply voltage, bias current, Tx and Rx
+	  optical power.  Calibration data is loaded from en7570-cal.bin or
+	  uploaded via the cal_data sysfs attribute.
+
+	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here.
